ComicInfo.Title: Door Prizes
ComicInfo.Summary:
Final issue of Volume 2! Voodoo stands at a crossroads. As she comes to grips with her past, what roles, if any, will Spartan, Jeremy and the rest of the Wildcats cast play in her future? And as this chapter in the Wildcats' saga ends, keep watching this space as the next, most unexpected, chapter begins!
